D\n\nThis game is a horror game with gorilla tag based locomotion. Traverse around.. What is it, a lab? I can't tell myself. The meat tunnels, and encounter\ncreatures that are... strange.. VERY very strange....", "short_description": "Where am I?"}]}, "developer_name": "MikeBite", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/lnfvr/privacy-policy?authuser=0", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "MikeBite", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/lnfvr/home?authuser=0", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "2691890164460465"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER"], "id": "7379336552165059"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1078184139959670"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1078184139959670"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1715620260, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1078184139959670"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "8466137080151662", "version": "0.1.4.7"}, "id": "1123969081955501", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7222467524518630", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_bi